---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro"

import HeroKeyBackground from "@/assets/hero-key-background.webp"
import LogoVI from "@/assets/eltiogloglo.png"
import FlechaAbajo from "@/assets/flecha-abajo.png"
import NuevaImagenBg from "@/assets/fondo-todo.png" 
import GlogloPerfil from "@/assets/gloglo-perfil2.jpg"
import GlogloSobreMi from "@/assets/gloglo-sobremi.png"
---

<Layout>
  <!-- CONTENEDOR DE LA LLUVIA DE MONEDAS -->
  <div id="lluvia-monedas" class="fixed inset-0 w-full h-screen pointer-events-none z-15 overflow-hidden"></div>

  <div id="logo-mask" class="fixed top-0 w-full h-screen bg-black z-10">
    <section>
      <picture
        id="hero-key"
        class="w-full h-screen scale-125 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden fixed bg-black"
      >
<div
          id="hero-key-logo"
          class="absolute z-10 max-w-[850px] w-full px-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center text-white md:items-end md:justify-center md:text-right md:pr-[0.5rem]"
        >
          <h1 class="text-white font-black tracking-wider uppercase text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-4xl drop-shadow-[0_2px_10px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)] mb-6 animate-pulse flex flex-col items-center md:items-end w-full leading-tight sm:leading-normal">
            <span>ELIMINA EL AZAR.</span>
            <span class="block">CONSTRUYE TU RIQUEZA.</span>
          </h1>

          <a 
            href="https://t.me/gloglokingbet" 
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-red-500 text-white font-black px-5 py-2.5 sm:px-6 sm:py-3 rounded-xl text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base uppercase tracking-wide hover:bg-red-600 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-red-500/20 transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 pointer-events-auto"
          >
            Unirse al Canal de Telegram
          </a>
        </div>

        <img
          id="hero-key-background"
          src={HeroKeyBackground.src}
          class="max-w-full max-h-full object-contain aspect-[1080/569]"
          alt="Background"
        />
      </picture>
    </section>
  </div>

<div 
    id="texto-bajo-gloglo" 
    class="fixed top-[52%] left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-25 w-full max-w-xl px-6 text-center text-white opacity-0 transform translate-y-8 pointer-events-none"
  >
    <h3 class="text-red-400 text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black uppercase tracking-[0.25em] drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(255,255,255,0.4)]">
      JUEGA A GANAR.
    </h3>

    <a 
      href="https://t.me/gloglokingbet" 
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-red-400 text-white font-black px-6 py-3 rounded-xl text-sm md:text-base uppercase tracking-wide hover:bg-red-600 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-red-500/20 transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 mt-8 pointer-events-auto" 
    >
      Unirse al Canal de Telegram
    </a>
  </div>

  <div
    class="fixed flex flex-col items-center justify-between h-screen px-20 py-16 w-full z-20 pointer-events-none"
  >
    <header class="flex justify-between items-center w-full pointer-events-auto">
      <a 
        href="https://kick.com/elglogloking" 
        target="_blank" 
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-block transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-110 cursor-pointer"
      >
        <img 
        id="LogoVI"
        src={LogoVI.src} 
        alt="Stake Logo"
        class="w-38 h-auto drop-shadow-[0_0_2px_rgba(255,255,255,.5),0_0_8px_#000]"
      />
      </a>

      <!-- BOTÓN MENÚ DE TRES RAYITAS -->
      <button 
        id="btn-open-menu"
        class="flex flex-col justify-between w-8 h-5 group cursor-pointer focus:outline-none z-50 select-none"
        aria-label="Abrir menú"
      >
        <span class="w-full h-[3px] bg-white rounded-full transition-transform duration-300 origin-left group-hover:bg-red-400"></span>
        <span class="w-full h-[3px] bg-white rounded-full transition-opacity duration-300 group-hover:bg-red-400"></span>
        <span class="w-full h-[3px] bg-white rounded-full transition-transform duration-300 origin-left group-hover:bg-red-400"></span>
      </button>
    </header>

<footer id="hero-footer" class="absolute bottom-8 m-auto">
      <img 
        src={FlechaAbajo.src} 
        alt="Flecha Abajo"
        class="w-38 h-auto drop-shadow-[0_0_2px_rgba(255,255,255,.5),0_0_8px_#000]"
      />
    </footer>
  </div>


  <div class="relative w-full min-h-[5000vh]">
    <!-- SEGUNDA SECCIÓN -->
<div 
  id="segunda-seccion" 
  class="fixed inset-0 w-full h-screen opacity-0 pointer-events-none bg-cover bg-center overflow-y-auto"
  style={`background-image: url(${NuevaImagenBg.src});`}
>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/70 z-0 pin-bg"></div>

  <!-- Contenedor Wrapper para centrado dinámico que permite scroll si el contenido supera la pantalla -->
  <div class="relative z-10 min-h-full w-full flex items-center justify-center py-12 md:py-20">
    
    <div 
      id="segunda-seccion-texto" 
      class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-12 opacity-0 transform translate-y-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-8 items-center text-left"
    >
      <!-- COLUMNA TEXTO -->
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center order-2 lg:order-1">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black uppercase tracking-wide mb-4 md:mb-6 text-white leading-tight drop-shadow-[0_4px_12px_rgba(0,0,0,0.6)]">
          Deja de buscar milagros. <br />
          <span class="text-red-400">Empieza a ver los datos.</span>
        </h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-3 md:space-y-4 max-w-xl text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg text-gray-300 font-medium leading-relaxed drop-shadow-[0_2px_4px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)]">
          <p>
            El mercado está lleno de capturas falsas. Por eso, <strong class="text-white font-bold">Las fijas</strong> creó un método diferente: análisis frío, gestión de riesgo y resultados verificados.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 font-light text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base">
            Aquí no apostamos por emoción, ejecutamos con estrategia para hacer crecer tu capital de forma inteligente. Las pruebas están sobre la mesa.
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-4 md:mt-6 text-white font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base border-l-4 border-red-400 pl-3">
          ¿Entras o te quedas mirando?
        </p>
        
        <div>
          <a 
            href="https://t.me/gloglokingbet" 
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-red-400 text-white font-black px-5 py-3 rounded-xl text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base uppercase tracking-wide hover:bg-red-600 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-red-500/20 transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 mt-6 md:mt-8 pointer-events-auto" 
          >
            Unirse al Canal de Telegram
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- COLUMNA TARJETA / IMAGEN -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-end w-full order-1 lg:order-2 mb-4 lg:mb-0">
        <!-- Se redujo la altura en móvil (h-[280px]) para que quepa perfectamente sin empujar demasiado el texto -->
        <div class="relative w-full max-w-[280px] sm:max-w-sm h-[280px] sm:h-[380px] md:h-[440px] flex items-center justify-center group">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-red-400/5 blur-3xl rounded-full scale-75 group-hover:bg-red-400/10 transition-all duration-750 pointer-events-none"></div>

          <!-- Tarjeta de fondo (Texto) -->
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-[80%] h-[80%] sm:h-[75%] rounded-xl border border-white/10 shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.6)] bg-neutral-950 p-4 sm:p-6 flex flex-col justify-between transition-all duration-500 group-hover:border-white/20 select-none">
            <div>
              <span class="text-[8px] sm:text-[10px] font-black tracking-widest text-red-400 uppercase block mb-0.5 sm:mb-1">CREADOR DE CONTENIDO</span>
              <h4 class="text-white font-black text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl tracking-wide uppercase">GLOGLOKING</h4>
              <p class="text-[9px] sm:text-[11px] md:text-xs text-gray-400 font-light italic mt-1 leading-relaxed tracking-wide max-w-[140px] sm:max-w-[180px]">
                "La minería me enseñó a buscar en lo oscuro; la disciplina me enseñó a brillar en lo más alto."
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4 sm:gap-8 border-t border-white/5 pt-3 sm:pt-4 text-left">
              <div>
                <span class="text-[8px] sm:text-[10px] text-gray-500 block uppercase tracking-wider mb-0.5">EFECTIVIDAD</span>
                <span class="text-base sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-emerald-400 font-black font-mono">95.6%</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-[8px] sm:text-[10px] text-gray-500 block uppercase tracking-wider mb-0.5">MÉTODO</span>
                <span class="text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base text-white font-bold tracking-wide block mt-0.5 sm:mt-1 font-mono">AUDITADO</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Tarjeta de frente (Foto) -->
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[55%] h-[65%] sm:h-[60%] rounded-lg overflow-hidden border-[3px] sm:border-[4px] border-neutral-900 shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.9)] bg-neutral-950 transform group-hover:translate-y-[-6px] group-hover:translate-x-[-6px] transition-transform duration-500 z-10">
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[2px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-red-400/40 to-transparent z-20"></div>
            <img 
              src={GlogloPerfil.src} 
              alt="Glogloking Perfil" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-95 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div 
      id="tercer-seccion" 
      class="fixed inset-0 w-full h-screen opacity-0 pointer-events-none bg-gradient-to-b from-black via-neutral-950 to-zinc-950 z-30 overflow-y-auto"
    >
      <div class="relative z-10 min-h-full w-full flex items-center justify-center py-12 md:py-16">
        
        <div class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center text-center px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-12">
          
          <h2 
            id="tercer-seccion-titulo" 
            class="font-black text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl uppercase tracking-wider mb-8 md:mb-10 opacity-0 transform translate-y-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-red-400 to-white bg-[length:200%_auto] bg-clip-text text-transparent select-none"
          >
            LO QUE NOS DIFERENCIA:
          </h2>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 w-full mb-8">
            <div class="tarjeta-unica border border-red-500/30 rounded-xl bg-neutral-950/60 backdrop-blur-md p-5 sm:p-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[220px] sm:min-h-[260px] opacity-0 transform translate-y-10 transition-all duration-300 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]">
              <div class="mb-3 md:mb-4 text-white">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="size-8 md:size-10 stroke-[1.25]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/><path d="M11 8v6"/><path d="M8 11h6"/></svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-white text-base md:text-xl font-black italic leading-relaxed mb-2">
                Acompañamiento Estratégico
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-xs md:text-base font-medium italic leading-relaxed px-2">
                 Guía continua las 24 horas para dominar el aspecto psicológico y no flaquear ante el mercado.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="tarjeta-unica border border-red-500/30 rounded-xl bg-neutral-950/60 backdrop-blur-md p-5 sm:p-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[220px] sm:min-h-[260px] opacity-0 transform translate-y-10 transition-all duration-300 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]">
              <div class="mb-3 md:mb-4 text-white">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="size-8 md:size-10 stroke-[1.25]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 7h-9"/><path d="M14 17H5"/><circle cx="17" cy="17" r="3"/><circle cx="7" cy="7" r="3"/></svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-white text-base md:text-xl font-black italic leading-relaxed mb-2">
                El Método VI
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-xs md:text-base font-medium italic leading-relaxed px-2">
                Una estructura basada en datos fríos, aplicable tanto a las canchas como a los escenarios virtuales de competencia.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="tarjeta-unica border border-red-500/30 rounded-xl bg-neutral-950/60 backdrop-blur-md p-5 sm:p-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[220px] sm:min-h-[260px] opacity-0 transform translate-y-10 transition-all duration-300 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]">
              <div class="mb-3 md:mb-4 text-white">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="size-8 md:size-10 stroke-[1.25]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="18" height="14" x="3" y="5" rx="2"/><path d="M12 5v14"/><path d="M3 12h18"/></svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-white text-base md:text-xl font-black italic leading-relaxed mb-2">
                Lectura Avanzada del Entorno
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-xs md:text-base font-medium italic leading-relaxed px-2">
                Datos exclusivos recopilados minuciosamente para evitar sorpresas y asegurar el control del juego.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="tarjeta-unica border border-red-500/30 rounded-xl bg-neutral-950/60 backdrop-blur-md p-5 sm:p-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[220px] sm:min-h-[260px] opacity-0 transform translate-y-10 transition-all duration-300 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]">
              <div class="mb-3 md:mb-4 text-white">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="size-8 md:size-10 stroke-[1.25]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22c5.523 0 10-4.477 10-10S17.523 2 12 2 2 6.477 2 12s4.477 10 10 10z"/><path d="m12 14-4-4h8z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-white text-base md:text-xl font-black italic leading-relaxed mb-2">
                Certeza Matemática
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-xs md:text-base font-medium italic leading-relaxed px-2">
                Expertos en datos descartando el ruido y seleccionando rigurosamente los 5 análisis diarios más sólidos.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p id="tercer-seccion-subtexto" class="text-white font-medium tracking-wide text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base mb-5 opacity-0 flex items-center justify-center gap-1">
            El poder del sol en la palma de tu mano 👇
          </p>

          <div>
            <a 
              id="btn-telegram"
              href="https://t.me/gloglokingbet" 
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#EF5350] text-black font-black px-6 py-3 sm:px-8 sm:py-3.5 rounded-md text-xs sm:text-base md:text-lg uppercase tracking-wide hover:bg-red-500 transition-colors pointer-events-auto shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(239,83,80,0.3)] opacity-0 transform scale-90"
            >
              Unirme al Canal Gratis
            </a>
          </div>
          
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- CUARTA SECCIÓN: VIDEO -->
    <div 
      id="cuarta-seccion-video" 
      class="fixed inset-0 w-full h-screen opacity-0 pointer-events-none bg-black z-40 overflow-hidden"
    >
      <video 
        id="video-scroll" 
        src="/src/assets/gloglo-box.mp4" 
        preload="auto" 
        muted 
        playsinline 
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      ></video>
      <div id="video-overlay" class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/0 transition-colors duration-300 pointer-events-none"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- QUINTA SECCIÓN: COMUNIDAD -->
    <div 
      id="quinta-seccion-comunidad" 
      class="fixed inset-0 w-full h-screen opacity-0 pointer-events-none flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 md:p-12 z-50"
    >
      <div class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <h2 id="voces-titulo" class="text-white font-black text-3xl md:text-6xl uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 opacity-0 transform translate-y-12 filter blur-[4px]">
          VOCES DE LA COMUNIDAD
        </h2>
        <p id="voces-subtitulo" class="text-red-400 font-bold tracking-widest text-xs md:text-sm uppercase mb-12 opacity-0 transform translate-y-6">
          Resultados reales de personas reales
        </p>

        <div id="voces-grid" class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 w-full opacity-0 transform translate-y-16">
          <div class="bg-neutral-950/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-xl text-left">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-red-400 font-black">C1</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-sm">Carlos M.</h4>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">Miembro desde hace 4 meses</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm italic font-light leading-relaxed">
              "Llevaba meses perdiendo dinero siguiendo a tipsters de capturas editadas. El método transparente de Gloglo me cambió el chip por completo."
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-neutral-950/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-xl text-left">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-red-400 font-black">A2</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-sm">Andrés R.</h4>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">Miembro VIP</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm italic font-light leading-relaxed">
              "Aquí aprendí a cuidar mi banca. No hay milagros, hay pura disciplina y análisis matemático frío de datos."
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-neutral-900/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-xl text-left">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-red-400 font-black">J3</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-sm">Juan Diego K.</h4>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">Comunidad de Kick</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm italic font-light leading-relaxed">
              "5 análisis al día y directo al grano, sin rodeos ni falsas promesas. El canal gratuito vale oro líquido."
            </p>
            
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a 
      href="https://t.me/gloglokingbet" 
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-red-400 text-white font-black px-6 py-3 rounded-xl text-sm md:text-base uppercase tracking-wide hover:bg-red-600 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-red-500/20 transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 mt-8 pointer-events-auto" 
    >
      Unirse al Canal de Telegram
    </a>
    </div>

    <!-- SEXTA SECCIÓN: SOBRE GLOGLOKING -->
<div 
      id="seccion-sobre-gloglo" 
      class="fixed inset-0 w-full h-screen opacity-0 pointer-events-none bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-neutral-500 z-[60] overflow-y-auto text-black"
    >
      <div class="relative z-10 min-h-full w-full flex items-center justify-center py-12 md:py-16">
        
        <div 
          id="sobre-gloglo-contenido" 
          class="max-w-6xl w-full mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-center opacity-0 transform translate-y-10"
        >
          <div class="w-full h-[240px] sm:h-[320px] md:h-[450px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border-4 border-neutral-100">
            <img 
              src={GlogloSobreMi.src} 
              alt="Sobre Glogloking" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col justify-center text-left">
            <span class="text-red-500 font-black tracking-widest text-[10px] sm:text-xs uppercase mb-1 md:mb-2">STREAMER Y CREADOR</span>
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mb-4 md:mb-6 text-neutral-900 leading-tight">
              SOBRE GLOGLOKING
            </h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-3 md:space-y-4 text-neutral-600 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                Detrás del éxito actual en las pantallas no hay un camino fácil, sino una historia de supervivencia. Antes de ser el streamer y creador de contenido que ves hoy, Glogloking conoció la oscuridad profunda de la minería: turnos interminables, explotación extrema y promesas rotas donde al final, nunca le pagaron nada por su esfuerzo.
              </p>
              <p class="text-neutral-700 font-light text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base">
                Ese dolor y esa injusticia se convirtieron en su mayor combustible. En lugar de rendirse, canalizó esa resistencia para dominar los mercados con frialdad matemática y construir su propia riqueza desde cero. Hoy, frente a miles de personas en vivo, su misión es limpiar el ruido del sistema, compartiendo de forma transparente las herramientas que a él lo sacaron del subsuelo absoluto.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

   <!-- SÉPTIMA SECCIÓN: RESULTADOS + CTA + FOOTER -->
    <div 
      id="seccion-resultados-final" 
     class="fixed inset-0 w-full h-screen opacity-0 pointer-events-none bg-gradient-to-b from-neutral-500 to-white z-[65] overflow-y-auto text-black flex flex-col justify-between"
    >
      <!-- CONTENIDO PRINCIPAL (RESULTADOS + CTA) -->
      <div class="w-full bg-transparent py-20 px-6 md:px-12 flex-grow">
        <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-32 text-center pt-6">
